    "EvaluationTable 3 and Fig. 6 present the experimental results for the popularity trend prediction tasks.",
    "The performance evaluation is based on the Rooted Mean Squared Error (RMSE) score and the Mean Absolute Percentage Error (MAPE):RMSE(y, ŷ) = N i=i (y i -ŷi) 2 N (23) MAPE(y, ŷ) = 1 N N i=i y i -ŷi y i, (24)which quantify the average difference between predicted values ŷ and actual values y of total N samples.",
